音乐场馆信托基金宣布“艺术家承诺”——呼吁艺人在达到舞台水平后回馈社会https://www.nme.com/news/music/music-venue-trust-announces-the-artist-pledge-calling-on-acts-to-give-back-when-they-reach-arena-level- 3758266?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=music-venue-trust-announces-the-artist-pledge-calling-acts-to-give-back-when-each-reach-arena-levelLiberty Dunworth Tue, 21 May 2024 14:43:36 +0000 Music NewsNews https://www.nme.com/?p=3758266 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Enter-Shikari@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Shikari 在伊利诺伊州芝加哥的舞台上表演。" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Enter-Shikari@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Enter-Shikari@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Enter-Shikari@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Enter-Shikari@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Enter-Shikari@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Enter-Shikari@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>超过 45 名艺术家已经签署了该承诺，其中包括 Frank Turner、The K&#39;s 和 Enter Shikari</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/music-venue-trust-announces-the-artist-pledge-calling-on-acts-to-give-back-when-they-reach-arena-level-3758266">音乐场馆信托基金会宣布“艺术家誓言”的帖子——呼吁艺人在达到舞台水平后回馈社会，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Enter-Shikari@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Shikari 在伊利诺伊州芝加哥的舞台上表演。" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Enter-Shikari@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Enter-Shikari@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Enter-Shikari@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Enter-Shikari@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Enter-Shikari@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Enter-Shikari@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>音乐场馆信托基金 (MVT) 宣布了“艺术家承诺”——一项呼吁艺人在达到舞台水平后回馈和支持基层场馆的活动。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/report-shows-disaster-facing-grassroots-music-venues-the-big-companies-and-arenas-are-now-going-to-have-to-answer-for-this-3576307">报告显示草根音乐场馆面临“灾难”：“大公司和场馆现在必须为此负责”</a></strong></li></ul><p>这一承诺的消息是在 MVT 发布<a href="https://www.musicvenuetrust.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/MVT_2023-Annual-Report_Digital.pdf?fbclid=IwAR2rm8d7s65E4d0ZHqNgvAnFIuVAA_CttOf5yqRKFR9onVTJPNkkwoKI4vk">2023 年该行业状况的完整报告之后发布的，该报告</a>显示<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/report-shows-disaster-facing-grassroots-music-venues-the-big-companies-and-arenas-are-now-going-to-have-to-answer-for-this-3576307">现场音乐面临着“灾难”，场馆以每周大约两个的速度关闭</a>。</p><p>在威斯敏斯特会议上，MVT 还呼应了他们的呼吁，即对<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-uks-new-arenas-respond-to-demand-to-invest-in-grassroots-music-venues-3391161">竞技场规模及以上的演出门票征税</a>，并要求主要唱片公司等回馈草根舞台，并认为“大公司现在将不得不为这”。</p><p>现在，随着今天（5 月 21 日）发布“艺术家誓言”，音乐场馆信托基金可以确认已有超过 45 名艺术家签署了该誓言，以确保每一位草根艺术家、场馆和发起人不仅能够生存，而且能够蓬勃发展。其中包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/frank-turner">Frank Turner</a> 、 <a href="/artists/the-ks">The K&#39;s</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-luka-state">The Luka State</a> 、Sister、Red Rum Club、 <a href="/artists/enter-shikari">Enter Shikari</a>等。</p><p>在活动中，MVT 要求艺术家们承诺，在他们取得成功的过程中，他们会承认自己来自哪里，并在达到舞台水平时向草根部门回馈少量资金。</p><p>在此之前，像 Enter Shikari 这样的多位艺术家回忆了在当地场馆演奏如何让他们取得成功，并宣布了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/enter-shikari-announce-2024-uk-arena-tour-in-support-of-music-venue-trust-buy-tickets-3438224">巡演的细节，其中每张售出的门票中的 1 英镑将捐赠给音乐场馆信托基金</a>。</p><p>从那时起， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-case-has-been-made-for-a-1-ticket-levy-on-all-arena-gigs-for-the-survival-of-grassroots-venues-and-artists-3611533">来自现场音乐行业的多位艺术家和人物随后前往议会，推动对所有舞台大小及以上的演出强制征收 1 英镑门票税</a>，包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/alien-ant-farm-cky-joint-uk-tour-with-1-ticket-levy-for-grassroots-venues-buy-tickets-3752024">Alien Ant Farm 和 CKY 在内的其他艺术家承诺帮助支持较小的场馆</a>他们即将举行的现场表演。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C7BghT9tQCY/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342